$interpreted: NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...*sob*...Nora-chan...Waaahhhh...
PAFF: Don't cry, NEKO...we did it.
PAFF: The people in this world are safe now...Nora...she'd be very happy about this too...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...*sobs*...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Hey, Aroma-chan, Nora-chan, she...also heard "that", right?
PAFF: ...Yes, I believe so.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: That song, it was rumbling around non-stop in my head...even now, it still hasn't stopped...
PAFF: "Humans shouldn't exist. Survive, destroy them all."
PAFF: That melody, it's seems to be repeating this message...
PAFF: I understand now. That is our origin. We...are all marionettes birthed from that rage.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Nora-chan knew about the truth earlier than all of us. Maybe...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: These voices, she's been hearing them all this time...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...It was so tough, yet she...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: If NEKO's was in her place...NEKO doesn't know if she'd have the courage to do that for the sake of everyone...
PAFF: I don't know either...But, NEKO, for Nora, and for the people of this world...
PAFF: There's one more thing...we can do together.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Together...?
???: ...I don't understand. Why would she go this far to prevent me from carrying out my duty...
Nolva: The damage you took is severe. In a few moments, you won't be able to move anymore. Stop thinking about those terrifying things, okay?
???: Destruction is a part of my preset supreme command. All my actions follow it as their principle.
???: Before I completely stop functioning, you cannot stop me from thinking this way.
Nolva: ...I think, all of this may just be an accident. The person who created you never intended for you to be like this.
Nolva: Or else, he wouldn't have sealed you away...
???: Are you a marionette maker as well?
???: ...Regardless, it has nothing to do with me now.
Nolva: Eh?
Ivy: That's my name...I think.

Ivy: This word is hidden in the deepest part of the core.
Not even the supreme command can interfere with its existence.
Ivy: I think, it...is related to the person most important to me.
Nolva: Why...are you telling me this?
Ivy: ...Because her actions triggered my feelings.
Ivy: No...perhaps, it's just that I...
Ivy: Wanted to do so.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Has she...shut down?
Nolva: Yes. Now, she can finally...
Nolva: ...be free from the marionettes' duty...
PAFF: ...It's about time we say goodbye.
Nolva: Eh?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: We've already discussed it. It's not like we can keep bothering you guys!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: After all, we aren't going back to Node 08 anyway. We might as well take some time off and go on a nice vacation...
Nolva: ...But, you have already remembered the command. Is it really okay for you to continue to go against it? Won't that be painful for you?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Nolva-chan...
Nolva: I'm also a marionette maker myself, so I know.
Nolva: When creating marionettes, the creator will tend to also design some kind of mechanism so the marionettes can't disobey orders.
Nolva: This is...our arrogance as a creator.
Nolva: ...Ugh...
PAFF: Miss Nolva, to be honest, I don't have memories of my past.
PAFF: The only thing I was told was to live as Aroma White. Even after becoming an idol, I still feel empty. Really empty...
PAFF: But now, I've found my answer. I can finally decide who I am, what lies ahead in my future.
PAFF: I...really like the way I am now.
Nolva: ......
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ahahahah, no worries, Nolva-chan!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Even though NEKO doesn't really believe NEKO is a marionette, NEKO is still NEKO! There's nothing to be afraid of!
Nolva: ...Miss NEKO, you've always been like this.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Teehee, what else do you expect?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ah, remember to help NEKO tell Kittyeyes, "Fight~ You will definitely get that steamy guy to fall for you one day~ I believe in you!"
Nolva: Understood. It's been a pleasure knowing you guys.
Nolva: Wish you all...the best of luck.
PAFF: If possible, I would like Miss Nolva to keep this a secret and not tell other people about us and what we experienced.
PAFF: As marionettes, we have memories from another world. We shouldn't interfere with everyone who lives in this world.
PAFF: This is my last request...please.
Nolva: Ah...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Aroma-chan, look!  I made an angel!
PAFF: You're amazing, NEKO!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Teehee~ When I was a child, I used to do this in sandpits.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: The white snow in this world is really pretty!
PAFF: Snow...I once sang a song about winter.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: For real? NEKO wants to hear it. Sing it for NEKO!
PAFF: Sure. Let me think...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Aroma-chan's singing really is amazing...
PAFF: I'm glad you like it, NEKO.

NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...Umm, NEKO seems a bit tired...
Aroma-chan, can you...stay by my side?
PAFF: No worries. I won't be going anywhere.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Hehe, Aroma-chan is the best...Goodnight...
PAFF: ...Goodnight, NEKO.
Nolva: It's alright, Waverlyde.
Nolva: I'm fine.
Nolva: ......It's just, I think I like their songs a bit too much.
